00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:05.000
one of the extremities of the fly,  on one of the legs of the fly.  And  

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:10.000
now, on one of the extremities of the fly, an ectopic eye will develop,   

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:15.000
