00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:19.000
by the mouse small eye gene.  What I'm telling you is that these  

00:04:19.000 --> 00:04:23.000
two genes are totally interchangeable,   

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:27.000
that they are effectively indistinguishable from one another,   

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:31.000
functionally they have some sequence relatedness, but in terms of the way  

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:34.000
